    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 344164.0,
      "end_time": 346529.0,
      "text": "annual coupon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 346529.0,
      "end_time": 347335.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s actually called,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 347335.0,
      "end_time": 348726.0,
      "text": "even though this is the interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 348726.0,
      "end_time": 351143.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m essentially going to pay $100 a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 351143.0,
      "end_time": 352900.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called a coupon because when they,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 352900.0,
      "end_time": 354612.0,
      "text": "when bonds were first issued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 354612.0,
      "end_time": 356671.0,
      "text": "they would actually throw these little coupons"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 356671.0,
      "end_time": 358695.0,
      "text": "on the bond itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 358695.0,
      "end_time": 360627.0,
      "text": "and the owner of the certificate could rip off"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 360627.0,
      "end_time": 362167.0,
      "text": "or cut off one of these coupons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 362167.0,
      "end_time": 365421.0,
      "text": "and then go to the person borrowing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 365421.0,
      "end_time": 366995.0,
      "text": "or the entity borrowing the money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 366995.0,
      "end_time": 368811.0,
      "text": "and get their actual interest payment."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 368811.0,
      "end_time": 370556.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why it&#39;s actually called &quot;coupons&quot;,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 370556.0,
      "end_time": 373012.0,
      "text": "but they don&#39;t actually attach those coupons anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 373012.0,
      "end_time": 374238.0,
      "text": "And it has some maturity date,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 374238.0,
      "end_time": 376464.0,
      "text": "the date that not only will I pay your interest back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 376464.0,
      "end_time": 378402.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ll pay the entire principle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 378402.0,
      "end_time": 379624.0,
      "text": "the entire face value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 379624.0,
      "end_time": 382565.0,
      "text": "so let&#39;s say the maturity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 382565.0,
      "end_time": 385633.0,
      "text": "maturity is in two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 385633.0,
      "end_time": 387057.0,
      "text": "is in two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 387057.0,
      "end_time": 388220.0,
      "text": "In this situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 388220.0,
      "end_time": 391158.0,
      "text": "in order to raise $5 million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 391158.0,
      "end_time": 394014.0,
      "text": "i&#39;m going to have to issue 5,000 of these"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 394014.0,
      "end_time": 398173.0,
      "text": "because 5,000 times 1,000 is 5 million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 398173.0,
      "end_time": 401741.0,
      "text": "so times 5,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 401741.0,
      "end_time": 405554.0,
      "text": "If you wanted to lend $1,000 to this company"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 405554.0,
      "end_time": 407126.0,
      "text": "so that they could expand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 407126.0,
      "end_time": 409058.0,
      "text": "and if you think 10% is a good interest rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 409058.0,
      "end_time": 410422.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a safe company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 410422.0,
      "end_time": 413099.0,
      "text": "you would essentially buy one of these bonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 413099.0,
      "end_time": 415668.0,
      "text": "Maybe you buy it for $1,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 415668.0,
      "end_time": 418582.0,
      "text": "and when you buy that bond for $1,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 418582.0,
      "end_time": 421357.0,
      "text": "you are essentially lending this company"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 421357.0,
      "end_time": 424750.0,
      "text": "that $1,000, and if you did that 5,000 times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 424750.0,
      "end_time": 426413.0,
      "text": "or if that happened 5,000 times"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 426413.0,
      "end_time": 427893.0,
      "text": "amongst a bunch of different people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 427893.0,
      "end_time": 429458.0,
      "text": "this company would be able to raise"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 429458.0,
      "end_time": 431828.0,
      "text": "its $5 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 431828.0,
      "end_time": 435126.0,
      "text": "Now just to be clear how the actual payments work."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 435126.0,
      "end_time": 438549.0,
      "text": "The coupons tend to get paid semi-annually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 438549.0,
      "end_time": 442160.0,
      "text": "so let me draw a little timeline here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 442160.0,
      "end_time": 443784.0,
      "text": "and this tends to be the case in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 443784.0,
      "end_time": 444753.0,
      "text": "and western Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 444753.0,
      "end_time": 447324.0,
      "text": "If this is today."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 447324.0,
      "end_time": 448642.0,
      "text": "This is today."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 448642.0,
      "end_time": 450815.0,
      "text": "This is in 6 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 450815.0,
      "end_time": 453629.0,
      "text": "This is in 12 months, or 1 year."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 453629.0,
      "end_time": 456857.0,
      "text": "This is in 18 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 456857.0,
      "end_time": 458834.0,
      "text": "and this is in 24 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 458834.0,
      "end_time": 460314.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m only going up to 24 months"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 460314.0,
      "end_time": 463828.0,
      "text": "because I said this bond matures in 24 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 463828.0,
      "end_time": 464617.0,
      "text": "What is this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 464617.0,
      "end_time": 468272.0,
      "text": "if you own, if you hold this bond, this certificate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 468272.0,
      "end_time": 469783.0,
      "text": "what do you get?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 469783.0,
      "end_time": 472329.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s going to pay you 10% annually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 472329.0,
      "end_time": 474520.0,
      "text": "so $100 a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 474520.0,
      "end_time": 476581.0,
      "text": "$100 per year."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 476581.0,
      "end_time": 478891.0,
      "text": "But they actually pay the coupons semi-annually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 478891.0,
      "end_time": 480127.0,
      "text": "so you get $100 a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 480127.0,
      "end_time": 482636.0,
      "text": "but you get half of it every 6 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 482636.0,
      "end_time": 485422.0,
      "text": "so you&#39;re going to get $50 after 6 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 485422.0,
      "end_time": 488067.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to get $50 after 12 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 488067.0,
      "end_time": 489494.0,
      "text": "or after another 6 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 489494.0,
      "end_time": 491116.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to get another $50 here."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 491116.0,
      "end_time": 493683.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to get a final $50 there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 493683.0,
      "end_time": 495693.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re also going to have to pay you back"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 495693.0,
      "end_time": 497338.0,
      "text": "the original amount of the loan."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 497338.0,
      "end_time": 500049.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re also going to have to pay you the $1,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 500049.0,
      "end_time": 502288.0,
      "text": "so that last payment&#39;s going to be the coupon of 50"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 502288.0,
      "end_time": 503968.0,
      "text": "plus the $1,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 503968.0,
      "end_time": 505833.0,
      "text": "and so you will have essentially been getting"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 505833.0,
      "end_time": 508221.0,
      "text": "this 10% annual interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 508221.0,
      "end_time": 509611.0,
      "text": "Now, when the company does this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 509611.0,
      "end_time": 511948.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ll probably have to issue some type of new bond"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 511948.0,
      "end_time": 512647.0,
      "text": "because all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 512647.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514116.00000000006,
      "text": "they have to pay all of these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 514116.0,
      "end_time": 516448.0,
      "text": "this huge lump sum of money"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 516448.0,
      "end_time": 517778.0,
      "text": "if they haven&#39;t been able to earn it"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 517778.0,
      "end_time": 518817.0,
      "text": "from the factories yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 518817.0,
      "end_time": 528817.0,
      "text": "and we could talk about that in a future video."
    }
  ]
}